  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Once per day as an immediate action, you can reroll any one d20 roll that you have just made before the results of the roll are revealed. You must take the result of the reroll, even if it's worse than the original roll.</p>\n<p>At 11th level, and every four levels thereafter, you can use this ability an additional time per day.</p>\n<p>You must be at least 7th level to select this revelation.</p>"
